Chapter 1
General information on data controlling
1.1 Information on the data controllers and the data protection officer:
The companies named below (each 100% subsidiary of Schön Klinik SE) offer services and
products to provide patients and users with care that is as low-threshold and frictionless
as possible and to provide various services for the detection, monitoring,
self-management and guideline-based treatment of mental illnesses.
For this purpose, the companies have concluded a contract on joint responsibility for the
processing of personal data in accordance with Art. 26 GDPR. For those areas where there is
no joint determination of the purposes and means of data processing, the respective named party
is the independent controller within the meaning of Art. 4 No. 7 GDPR.
This privacy policy applies to data processing by the following companies:
