3.2.5 Hosting & Data Center
MindDoc Healthcare uses the Schön Klinik Holding SE, Balanstraße 71a, 81451 Munich, for the operation and maintenance of the practice management system. The Schön Klinik
Holding SE therefore processes your patient data on behalf of and strictly in accordance with the instructions of MindDoc Healthcare for the documentation and archiving of the course of treatment.
